text: Eugène G. Grisot was an archer from France. He was born on 19 December 1866 and died on 2 May 1936. Grisot competed at the 1908 Summer Olympics and the 1920 Summer Olympics.Eugène Grisot == References == Category:1866 births Category:1936 deaths Category:French archers Category:Olympic gold medalists for France Category:Olympic silver medalists for France Category:Olympic bronze medalists for France
